column9:
Éducatrice allemande de la petite enfance;
Certificats et références écrits disponible; 
Nanny/Nounou expérimentée dans les famille VIP (formelle et informelle);
Langue parlant sont allemand, anglais et français;

Discrète, sérieuse, patiente, flexible, fidèle, calme,

BONJOUR

Ayant une longue expérience en milieu hospitalier et gériatrique, j'ai aussi 2 années de formation en soins infirmiers validées;
aussi je serai heureuse d'etre employée comme auxiliaire de vie, ou aide soignante chez un particulier;
volontaire, j'aime contribuer au bien -etre des personnes dont j'ai la prise en charge;
dévouée, je suis à l'écoute des besoins des personnes dont je m'occupe et veille à satisfaire les besoins des personnes;

Dear parents:


Capitalizing on my success in managing the needs of children of different ages, I am seeking a professional opportunity where my experience and dedication can benefit your family. As a dependable, caring and calm nanny who has over 10 years of childcare experience, working for multiple families in Washington DC, New York and Boston, I believe myself to be a strong candidate for the position of governess for your children.

A brief highlight of the skills and values I would be adding by joining your family follows:

● Highly vigilant and alert professional with a verifiable track record of ensuring the children’s physical safety;
● Familiar with children’s age specific developmental, cognitive and psychosocial needs;
● Well-versed in assisting children with their home work and accompanying them to social visits; 
● Competent at performing housekeeping tasks; meal preparation, cleaning, laundry and grocery shopping; 
● Expert in imparting self care skills and maintaining a hygienic and nurturing environment for children. 

Find enclosed my resume. I would welcome an interview with you to further explore the merging of my competencies and experience with your needs.

Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to speaking with you soon.

Best regards,

Elena CHOBANOVA

nous sommes  a votre disposition pour tout renseignement complementaire;
cordialement
eric lagrave

